n></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\nSmelt een klont boter in een soepketel.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2018/02/26/ff541d17-1b0c-11e8-abcc-02b7b76bf47f.png\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-301080\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nStoof de grof gesneden uien aan. Hou de fijngesneden uien apart.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2018/02/26/21080b19-1b0d-11e8-abcc-02b7b76bf47f.png\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-301081\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n<div class=\"ingredients-as-text-wrapper\" data-ingredients-as-text-wrapper=\"\" data-ingredients=\"[{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:5,&quot;unit&quot;:null,&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;wortel&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;wortelen&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Groenten en fruit&quot;}}]\">\r\n<ul class=\"ingredients-as-text\" aria-label=\"ingredienten\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">5 wortelen</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\nSchil de wortelen en snijd ze in stukken. Stoof ze met de ui in de soepketel.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"ad-container\" data-max-width=\"959\">\r\n<div class=\"pebble-ad js-pebble-ad js-pebble-leaderboard\" data-format=\"leaderboard\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2018/02/26/00600ed8-1b0d-11e8-abcc-02b7b76bf47f.png\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-301082\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n<div class=\"ingredients-as-text-wrapper\" data-ingredients-as-text-wrapper=\"\" data-ingredients=\"[{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:2,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;tenen&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;tenen&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;knoflook&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;knoflook&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Olie, azijn en specerijen&quot;}}]\">\r\n<ul class=\"ingredients-as-text\" aria-label=\"ingredienten\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">2 tenen knoflook</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\nKneus en pel de knoflook. Snijd de tenen in stukken en stoof ze mee aan.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-tip\"><span class=\"preparation-tip__icon\"><i class=\"far fa-lightbulb\"></i>TIP</span>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-tip__content\">De knoflook is optioneel. Als je liever geen knoflook eet, laat je hem gewoon weg.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2018/02/26/22052fca-1b0d-11e8-abcc-02b7b76bf47f.png\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-301084\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n<div class=\"ingredients-as-text-wrapper\" data-ingredients-as-text-wrapper=\"\" data-ingredients=\"[{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:0,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;enkele takjes&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;enkele takjes&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;tijm&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;tijm&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Olie, azijn en specerijen&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:0,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;enkele takjes&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;enkele takjes&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;rozemarijn&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;rozemarijn&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Olie, azijn en specerijen&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:0,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;enkele blaadjes&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;enkele blaadjes&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;laurier&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;laurier&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Kruidenierswaren&quot;}}]\">\r\n<ul class=\"ingredients-as-text\" aria-label=\"ingredienten\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">enkele takjes tijm</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">enkele takjes rozemarijn</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">enkele blaadjes laurier</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\nBind de tijm, laurier en rozemarijn samen met keukentouw tot een bouquet garni. Leg het in de soep.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-301085\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n<div class=\"ingredients-as-text-wrapper\" data-ingredients-as-text-wrapper=\"\" data-ingredients=\"[{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:1,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;fles&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;flessen&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;rode wijn&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;rode wijn&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Alcoholische dranken&quot;}}]\">\r\n<ul class=\"ingredients-as-text\" aria-label=\"ingredienten\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">1 fles rode wijn</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\nGiet er de wijn bij en laat even goed doorkoken zodat de alcohol verdampt.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2018/02/26/44f483fc-1b0d-11e8-abcc-02b7b76bf47f.png\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-301086\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n<div class=\"ingredients-as-text-wrapper\" data-ingredients-as-text-wrapper=\"\" data-ingredients=\"[{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;(fles)&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:1360,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;g&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;g&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;passata&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;passata&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Sauzen en condimenten&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;(blik)&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;gepelde&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:800,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;g&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;g&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;tomaat&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;tomaten&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Groenten en fruit&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:1,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;liter&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;l&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;water&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;water&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Non alcoholische dranken&quot;}}]\">\r\n<ul class=\"ingredients-as-text\" aria-label=\"ingredienten\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">1360 g passata (fles)</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">800 g gepelde tomaten (blik)</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">1 liter water</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\nDoe de passata en de gepelde tomaten bij de soep. Giet er het water bij en zet een deksel op de soepketel. Laat 30 minuten garen op een zacht vuur.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step is-active\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2018/02/26/68dc1add-1b0d-11e8-abcc-02b7b76bf47f.png\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-301087\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n<div class=\"ingredients-as-text-wrapper\" data-ingredients-as-text-wrapper=\"\" data-ingredients=\"[{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:0,&quot;unit&quot;:null,&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;boter&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;boter&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Zuivel&quot;}}]\">\r\n<ul class=\"ingredients-as-text\" aria-label=\"ingredienten\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">boter</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\nSmelt een klont boter in een hoge pan. Bak de apart gehouden uien mooi bruin in de boter. Ze zijn het lekkerst als ze wat gekaramelliseerd zijn.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2018/02/26/6a197cde-1b0d-11e8-abcc-02b7b76bf47f.png\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-301088\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n<div class=\"ingredients-as-text-wrapper\" data-ingredients-as-text-wrapper=\"\" data-ingredients=\"[{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:200,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;g&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;g&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;gerookt spek&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;gerookt spek&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Vleeswaren&quot;}}]\">\r\n<ul class=\"ingredients-as-text\" aria-label=\"ingredienten\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">200 g gerookt spek</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\nSnijd het spek in reepjes. Bak het in een andere pan krokant. Laat uitlekken op keukenpapier.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2018/02/26/6b22615f-1b0d-11e8-abcc-02b7b76bf47f.png\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-301089\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nHaal het bouquet garni uit de soep. Mix de soep met de staafmixer.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2018/02/26/b0232ce6-1b0d-11e8-abcc-02b7b76bf47f.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-301090\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nDoe de gebakken uien en het spek bij de soep. Geef er brood bij.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Uien- en tomatensoep met spek','Jeroen kreeg dit recept voor tomatensoep van Quinten, een Vlaamse chef die in Lapland werkt. Hij doet er spekjes en gebakken ui bij als garnituur. Heerlijk voor als het ijskoud is.','publish','closed','closed','','uien-en-tomatensoep-met-spek','','','2018-10-07 15:24:32','2018-10-07 13:24:32','',0,'http://localhost/?post_type=recipe&#038;p=108',0,'recipe','',0),(109,1,'2018-10-07 15:24:32','2018-10-07 13:24:32','<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2018/02/26/fd5df265-1b0c-11e8-abcc-02b7b76bf47f.png\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-301078\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n<div class=\"ingredients-as-text-wrapper\" data-ingredients-as-text-wrapper=\"\" data-ingredients=\