 soep. Mix de soep met de staafmixer.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2018/02/26/b0232ce6-1b0d-11e8-abcc-02b7b76bf47f.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-301090\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nDoe de gebakken uien en het spek bij de soep. Geef er brood bij.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Uien- en tomatensoep met spek','Jeroen kreeg dit recept voor tomatensoep van Quinten, een Vlaamse chef die in Lapland werkt. Hij doet er spekjes en gebakken ui bij als garnituur. Heerlijk voor als het ijskoud is.','inherit','closed','closed','','108-revision-v1','','','2018-10-07 15:24:32','2018-10-07 13:24:32','',108,'http://localhost/2018/10/108-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(110,1,'2018-10-07 15:30:21','2018-10-07 13:30:21','<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296282\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n<div class=\"ingredients-as-text-wrapper\" data-ingredients-as-text-wrapper=\"\" data-ingredients=\"[{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;(met of zonder bot)&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:500,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;g&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;g&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;soepvlees&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;soepvlees&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Vleeswaren&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;(uit blik)&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;hele&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:1600,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;g&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;g&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;tomaat&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;tomaten&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Groenten en fruit&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:4,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;stengel&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;stengels&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;selder&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;selder&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Groenten en fruit&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:3,&quot;unit&quot;:null,&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;ui&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;uien&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Groenten en fruit&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:3,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;teentje&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;teentjes&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;look&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;look&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Groenten en fruit&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;(kleine)&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:3,&quot;unit&quot;:null,&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;wortel&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;wortelen&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Groenten en fruit&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:2,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;takje&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;takjes&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;rozemarijn&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;rozemarijn&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Olie, azijn en specerijen&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:4,&quot;unit&quot;:null,&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;laurierblaadje&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;laurierblaadjes&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Kruidenierswaren&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:4,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;takje&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;takjes&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;tijm&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;tijm&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Olie, azijn en specerijen&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:0,&quot;unit&quot;:null,&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;peterseliestelen&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;peterseliestelen&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Groenten en fruit&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;(geconcentreerd)&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:70,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;g&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;g&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;tomatenpuree&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;tomatenpuree&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Conserven&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;(riet)&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:1,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;eetlepel&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;eetlepels&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;suiker&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;suiker&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Kruidenierswaren&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:0,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;scheutje&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;scheutjes&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;olijfolie&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;olijfolie&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Olie, azijn en specerijen&quot;}}]\">\r\n<ul class=\"ingredients-as-text\" aria-label=\"ingredienten\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">500 g soepvlees (met of zonder bot)</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">1600 g hele tomaten (uit blik)</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">4 stengels selder</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">3 uien</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">3 teentjes look</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">3 (kleine) wortelen</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">2 takjes rozemarijn</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">4 laurierblaadjes</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">4 takjes tijm</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">peterseliestelen</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">70 g tomatenpuree (geconcentreerd)</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">1 eetlepel (riet) suiker</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">scheutjes olijfolie</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\nPel de uien en snij ze in grove stukken.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296283\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nSpoel de stengels selder en schil de wortelen. Snij beide groenten ook in grove stukken.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296284\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nVerhit een scheut olijfolie in een ruime stoofpot of soepketel op een matig vuur. Stoof de uien kort en voeg dan alle andere groenten toe.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"ad-container\" data-max-width=\"959\">\r\n<div class=\"pebble-ad js-pebble-ad js-pebble-leaderboard\" data-format=\"leaderboard\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/809c9a3b-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296285\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nPel de looktenen, snij ze grof en roer de stukjes door de stovende groenten.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/810917ac-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296286\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nVerzamel de rozemarijn, de takjes tijm en de laurierblaadjes. Doe er eventueel ook peterseliestelen bij. Bind alle kruiden samen tot een grote ‘bouquet garni’.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-tip__icon\"><i class=\"fas fa-question\"></i>KOOKVRAAG</div>\r\n<a class=\"preparation-tip\" href=\"https://dagelijksekost.een.be/kookvragen/hoe-maak-ik-een-bouquet-garni\"> </a>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-tip__content\">Hoe maak ik een bouquet garni?</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/816e903d-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296288\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nGooi de kruidentuil in de pot, roer en zet het vuur wat zachter. Roer de tomatenpuree door de groenten en laat het concentraat kort bakken.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296289\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nGiet de hele tomaten uit blik in de pot. Voeg ook evenveel water toe. Roer eventuele bakresten op de bodem van de pot los.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-tip\">\r\n\r\n<span class=\"preparation-tip__icon\"><i class=\"far fa-lightbulb\"></i>TIP</span>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-tip__content\">Gebruik het water om de blikken uit te spoelen, alvorens het in de soep gaat.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/81cd520e-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296291\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nLeg het stuk soepvlees in de soep, voeg een klein beetje suiker toe en zet het deksel op de pot.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/822d736f-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296292\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nLaat de soep één tot twee uur pruttelen op een zacht vuur. (Liefst tot het soepvlees mals is, zodat je het later kan verwerken in een andere bereiding.)\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"dish-preparation__subtitle preparation-subtitle headline-3\">Voor véél gehaktballetjes</h3>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/828ef460-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296293\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n<div class=\"ingredients-as-text-wrapper\" data-ingredients-as-text-wrapper=\"\" data-ingredients=\"[{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:750,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;g&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;g&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;gemengd gehakt&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;gemengd gehakt&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Vleeswaren&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:2,&quot;unit&quot;:null,&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;ei&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;eieren&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Zuivel&quot;}}]\">\r\n<ul class=\"ingredients-as-text\" aria-label=\"ingredienten\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">750 g gemengd gehakt</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">2 eieren</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\nDoe het gehakt in een ruime mengschaal en voeg de eieren toe. Meng ze zorgvuldig door het vlees.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/83038821-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296294\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n<div class=\"ingredients-as-text-wrapper\" data-ingredients-as-text-wrapper=\"\" data-ingredients=\"[{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:50,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;g&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;g&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;paneermeel&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;paneermeel&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Kruidenierswaren&quot;}}]\">\r\n<ul class=\"ingredients-as-text\" aria-label=\"ingredienten\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">50 g paneermeel</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\nStrooi wat paneermeel bij het vlees en meng tot je een stevig maar tegelijk smeuïg gehaktmengsel hebt.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/837360f2-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296295\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nSpoel je handen en hou ze nat om de balletjes te rollen. Dan gaat het eens zo makkelijk. Rol balletjes met een diameter van ongeveer anderhalve centimeter.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/83eadae3-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296296\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nGooi ze in de hete soep en laat het vlees enkele minuten garen.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/84555c84-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296297\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nSchep de gehaktballetjes uit de soep en verzamel ze in een kom. Laat ze even uitlekken.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/84be3075-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296298\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n<div class=\"ingredients-as-text-wrapper\" data-ingredients-as-text-wrapper=\"\" data-ingredients=\"[{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;maar mag ook een klontje boter zijn&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:0,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;scheutje&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;scheutjes&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;olijfolie&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;olijfolie&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Olie, azijn en specerijen&quot;}}]\">\r\n<ul class=\"ingredients-as-text\" aria-label=\"ingredienten\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">scheutjes olijfolie maar mag ook een klontje boter zijn</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\nVerhit een braadpan op een matig vuur. Schenk er een scheut olijfolie in, of gebruik wat boter. Bak de balletjes tot ze een goudbruin korstje hebben.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-tip\">\r\n\r\n<span class=\"preparation-tip__icon\"><i class=\"far fa-lightbulb\"></i>TIP</span>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-tip__content\">Grote hoeveelheden balletjes bak je best in meerdere beurten.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"dish-preparation__subtitle preparation-subtitle headline-3\">Afwerken en serveren</h3>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/85551946-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296300\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nVerwijder de uitgekookte kruidentuil uit de soep. Schep ook het soepvlees eruit.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/85b78498-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296301\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nMix de tomatensoep glad met de staafmixer. Schep ze daarna door een grote zeef.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/8613d569-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296302\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nRoer de soep in delen door de zeef met de bolle zijde van een (kleine) pollepel. De droge pulp gooi je weg.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/8688692a-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296303\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n<div class=\"ingredients-as-text-wrapper\" data-ingredients-as-text-wrapper=\"\" data-ingredients=\"[{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;van de molen&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:0,&quot;unit&quot;:null,&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;peper&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;peper&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Olie, azijn en specerijen&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:0,&quot;unit&quot;:null,&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;zout&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;zout&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Olie, azijn en specerijen&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:0,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;snuifje&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;snuifjes&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;cayennepeper&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;cayennepeper&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Olie, azijn en specerijen&quot;}}]\">\r\n<ul class=\"ingredients-as-text\" aria-label=\"ingredienten\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">peper van de molen</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">zout</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">snuifjes cayennepeper</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\nRoer, proef en kruid de soep naar smaak met versgemalen peper, eventueel een snuifje cayennepeper en wat zout.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/86f8901b-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296304\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nBreng de soep opnieuw aan de kook op een zacht vuur. Voeg er ook de gebakken soepballetjes bij.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Tomatensoep met veel balletjes','Tomatensoepje voor de liefhebbers','publish','closed','closed','','tomatensoep-met-veel-balletjes','','','2018-10-07 15:30:21','2018-10-07 13:30:21','',0,'http://localhost/?post_type=recipe&#038;p=110',0,'recipe','',0),(111,1,'2018-10-07 15:30:21','2018-10-07 13:30:21','<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296282\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n<div class=\"ingredients-as-text-wrapper\" data-ingredients-as-text-wrapper=\"\" data-ingredients=\"[{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;(met of zonder bot)&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:500,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;g&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;g&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;soepvlees&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;soepvlees&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Vleeswaren&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;(uit blik)&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;hele&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:1600,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;g&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;g&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;tomaat&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;tomaten&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Groenten en fruit&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:4,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;stengel&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;stengels&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;selder&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;selder&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Groenten en fruit&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:3,&quot;unit&quot;:null,&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;ui&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;uien&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Groenten en fruit&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:3,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;teentje&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;teentjes&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;look&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;look&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Groenten en fruit&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;(kleine)&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:3,&quot;unit&quot;:null,&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;wortel&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;wortelen&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Groenten en fruit&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:2,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;takje&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;takjes&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;rozemarijn&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;rozemarijn&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Olie, azijn en specerijen&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:4,&quot;unit&quot;:null,&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;laurierblaadje&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;laurierblaadjes&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Kruidenierswaren&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:4,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;takje&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;takjes&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;tijm&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;tijm&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Olie, azijn en specerijen&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:0,&quot;unit&quot;:null,&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;peterseliestelen&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;peterseliestelen&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Groenten en fruit&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;(geconcentreerd)&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:70,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;g&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;g&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;tomatenpuree&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;tomatenpuree&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Conserven&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;(riet)&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:1,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;eetlepel&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;eetlepels&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;suiker&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;suiker&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Kruidenierswaren&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:0,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;scheutje&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;scheutjes&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;olijfolie&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;olijfolie&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Olie, azijn en specerijen&quot;}}]\">\r\n<ul class=\"ingredients-as-text\" aria-label=\"ingredienten\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">500 g soepvlees (met of zonder bot)</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">1600 g hele tomaten (uit blik)</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">4 stengels selder</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">3 uien</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">3 teentjes look</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">3 (kleine) wortelen</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">2 takjes rozemarijn</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">4 laurierblaadjes</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">4 takjes tijm</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">peterseliestelen</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">70 g tomatenpuree (geconcentreerd)</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">1 eetlepel (riet) suiker</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">scheutjes olijfolie</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\nPel de uien en snij ze in grove stukken.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296283\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nSpoel de stengels selder en schil de wortelen. Snij beide groenten ook in grove stukken.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296284\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nVerhit een scheut olijfolie in een ruime stoofpot of soepketel op een matig vuur. Stoof de uien kort en voeg dan alle andere groenten toe.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"ad-container\" data-max-width=\"959\">\r\n<div class=\"pebble-ad js-pebble-ad js-pebble-leaderboard\" data-format=\"leaderboard\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/809c9a3b-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296285\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nPel de looktenen, snij ze grof en roer de stukjes door de stovende groenten.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/810917ac-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296286\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nVerzamel de rozemarijn, de takjes tijm en de laurierblaadjes. Doe er eventueel ook peterseliestelen bij. Bind alle kruiden samen tot een grote ‘bouquet garni’.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-tip__icon\"><i class=\"fas fa-question\"></i>KOOKVRAAG</div>\r\n<a class=\"preparation-tip\" href=\"https://dagelijksekost.een.be/kookvragen/hoe-maak-ik-een-bouquet-garni\"> </a>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-tip__content\">Hoe maak ik een bouquet garni?</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/816e903d-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296288\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nGooi de kruidentuil in de pot, roer en zet het vuur wat zachter. Roer de tomatenpuree door de groenten en laat het concentraat kort bakken.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296289\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nGiet de hele tomaten uit blik in de pot. Voeg ook evenveel water toe. Roer eventuele bakresten op de bodem van de pot los.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-tip\">\r\n\r\n<span class=\"preparation-tip__icon\"><i class=\"far fa-lightbulb\"></i>TIP</span>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-tip__content\">Gebruik het water om de blikken uit te spoelen, alvorens het in de soep gaat.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/81cd520e-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296291\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nLeg het stuk soepvlees in de soep, voeg een klein beetje suiker toe en zet het deksel op de pot.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/822d736f-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296292\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nLaat de soep één tot twee uur pruttelen op een zacht vuur. (Liefst tot het soepvlees mals is, zodat je het later kan verwerken in een andere bereiding.)\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"dish-preparation__subtitle preparation-subtitle headline-3\">Voor véél gehaktballetjes</h3>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/828ef460-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296293\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n<div class=\"ingredients-as-text-wrapper\" data-ingredients-as-text-wrapper=\"\" data-ingredients=\"[{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:750,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;g&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;g&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;gemengd gehakt&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;gemengd gehakt&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Vleeswaren&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:2,&quot;unit&quot;:null,&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;ei&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;eieren&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Zuivel&quot;}}]\">\r\n<ul class=\"ingredients-as-text\" aria-label=\"ingredienten\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">750 g gemengd gehakt</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">2 eieren</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\nDoe het gehakt in een ruime mengschaal en voeg de eieren toe. Meng ze zorgvuldig door het vlees.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/83038821-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296294\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n<div class=\"ingredients-as-text-wrapper\" data-ingredients-as-text-wrapper=\"\" data-ingredients=\"[{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:50,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;g&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;g&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;paneermeel&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;paneermeel&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Kruidenierswaren&quot;}}]\">\r\n<ul class=\"ingredients-as-text\" aria-label=\"ingredienten\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">50 g paneermeel</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\nStrooi wat paneermeel bij het vlees en meng tot je een stevig maar tegelijk smeuïg gehaktmengsel hebt.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/837360f2-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296295\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nSpoel je handen en hou ze nat om de balletjes te rollen. Dan gaat het eens zo makkelijk. Rol balletjes met een diameter van ongeveer anderhalve centimeter.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/83eadae3-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296296\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nGooi ze in de hete soep en laat het vlees enkele minuten garen.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/84555c84-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296297\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nSchep de gehaktballetjes uit de soep en verzamel ze in een kom. Laat ze even uitlekken.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/84be3075-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296298\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n<div class=\"ingredients-as-text-wrapper\" data-ingredients-as-text-wrapper=\"\" data-ingredients=\"[{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;maar mag ook een klontje boter zijn&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:0,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;scheutje&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;scheutjes&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;olijfolie&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;olijfolie&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Olie, azijn en specerijen&quot;}}]\">\r\n<ul class=\"ingredients-as-text\" aria-label=\"ingredienten\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">scheutjes olijfolie maar mag ook een klontje boter zijn</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\nVerhit een braadpan op een matig vuur. Schenk er een scheut olijfolie in, of gebruik wat boter. Bak de balletjes tot ze een goudbruin korstje hebben.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-tip\">\r\n\r\n<span class=\"preparation-tip__icon\"><i class=\"far fa-lightbulb\"></i>TIP</span>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-tip__content\">Grote hoeveelheden balletjes bak je best in meerdere beurten.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"dish-preparation__subtitle preparation-subtitle headline-3\">Afwerken en serveren</h3>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/85551946-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296300\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nVerwijder de uitgekookte kruidentuil uit de soep. Schep ook het soepvlees eruit.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/85b78498-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296301\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nMix de tomatensoep glad met de staafmixer. Schep ze daarna door een grote zeef.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/8613d569-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296302\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nRoer de soep in delen door de zeef met de bolle zijde van een (kleine) pollepel. De droge pulp gooi je weg.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/8688692a-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296303\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n<div class=\"ingredients-as-text-wrapper\" data-ingredients-as-text-wrapper=\"\" data-ingredients=\"[{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;van de molen&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:0,&quot;unit&quot;:null,&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;peper&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;peper&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Olie, azijn en specerijen&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:0,&quot;unit&quot;:null,&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;zout&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;zout&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Olie, azijn en specerijen&quot;}},{&quot;append&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;prepend&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;:0,&quot;unit&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;snuifje&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;snuifjes&quot;},&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;cayennepeper&quot;,&quot;plural&quot;:&quot;cayennepeper&quot;,&quot;aisle&quot;:&quot;Olie, azijn en specerijen&quot;}}]\">\r\n<ul class=\"ingredients-as-text\" aria-label=\"ingredienten\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">peper van de molen</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">zout</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"inline-ingredient\">snuifjes cayennepeper</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\nRoer, proef en kruid de soep naar smaak met versgemalen peper, eventueel een snuifje cayennepeper en wat zout.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dish-preparation__step preparation-step js-preparation-step\" data-dish-preparation-step=\"\" data-dish-preparation-step-image=\"https://images.vrt.be/dako2017_1600s_j75/2017/03/06/86f8901b-0252-11e7-8f5f-00163edf48dd.jpg\" data-dish-preparation-step-id=\"step-296304\">\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__number\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"preparation-step__content\">\r\n\r\nBreng de soep opnieuw aan de kook op een zacht vuur. Voeg er ook de gebakken soepballetjes bij.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Tomatensoep met veel balletjes','Tomatensoepje voor de liefhebbers','inherit','closed','closed','','110-revision-v1','','','2018-10-07 15:30:21','2018-10-07 13:30:21','',110,'http://localhost/2018/10/110-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(112,1,'2018-10-07 15:41:59','2018-10-07 13:41:59','<ol>\r\n 	<li>Pel en snipper de ui en de knoflook. Stoof ze glazig in olie. Voeg beetje bij beetje het gehakt toe en bak het rul.</li>\r\n 	<li>Voeg het basilicum, de oregano, chilivlokken, het bouillonblokje, worcestershiresaus en suiker toe. Doe er vervolgens de tomatenblokjes, tomatenpuree, 100 ml water en de diepvriesspinazie bij. Laat op een zacht vuurtje 30 minuten sudderen, roer regelmatig om.</li>\r\n 	<li>Verwarm de oven voor op 200°C. Kook de penne beetgaar in gezouten water, volgens de aanwijzingen op de verpakking. Giet de pasta af.</li>\r\n 	<li>Meng de penne met de saus en doe de pasta in een ingevette ovenschaal. Strooi er beide kaassoorten over en zet 25 minuten in de oven, tot de kaas gesmolten en mooi goudbruin is. Serveer met wat stokbrood en eventueel nog wat verse kruiden.</li>\r\n</ol>','','','publish','closed','closed','','112','','','2018-10-07 15:41:59','2018-10-07 13:41:59','',0,'http://localhost/?post_type=recipe&#038;p=112',0,'recipe','',0),(113,1,'2018-10-07 15:41:59','2018-10-07 13:41:59','<ol>\r\n 	<li>Pel en snipper de ui en de knoflook. Stoof ze glazig in olie. Voeg beetje bij beetje het gehakt toe en bak het rul.</li>\r\n 	<li>Voeg het basilicum, de oregano, chilivlokken, het bouillonblokje, worcestershiresaus en suiker toe. Doe er vervolgens de tomatenblokjes, tomatenpuree, 100 ml water en de diepvriesspinazie bij. Laat op een zacht vuurtje 30 minuten sudderen, roer regelmatig om.</li>\r\n 	<li>Verwarm de oven voor op 200°C. Kook de penne beetgaar in gezouten water, volgens de aanwijzingen op de verpakking. Giet de pasta af.</li>\r\n 	<li>Meng de penne met de saus en doe de pasta in een ingevette ovenschaal. Strooi er beide kaassoorten over en zet 25 minuten in de oven, tot de kaas gesmolten en mooi goudbruin is. Serveer met wat stokbrood en eventueel nog wat verse kruiden.</li>\r\n</ol>','','','inherit','closed','closed','','112-revision-v1','','','2018-10-07 15:41:59','2018-10-07 13:41:59','',112,'http://localhost/2018/10/112-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
